  <driver id="homematic">
    <name>HomeMaticDriver</name>
    <description><![CDATA[
    	The HomeMatic Driver implements a serial or usb connection to homematic devices as there are 
    	CO2Detectors, MotionDetectors, PowerMeters, RemoteDevices, SmokeSensors, SwitchPlugs, Thermostats, 
    	ThreeStateSensors, THSensors. The serial connection is based on the asksin protokol. The protocol 
    	of the usb connection is unknown and not tested yet.
      ]]>
